      "writtenOn": "2020-10-20T22:28:00Z",
      "side": 1,
      "message": "I\u0027m not familiar with C++ coding style, but I see method with upper case names and others with lower case names (e.g. \"metadata()\" vs \"LoadFrom()\").\n\nShouldn\u0027t all method names be lowerCamelCase? (we should be good citizens and follow the style of the code around us).\n\nhttps://source.corp.google.com/android/external/qemu/android/docs/ANDROID-CODING-STYLE.md",
      "revId": "d475b5651fd4255a975a3aab4aa2d17b49a96a20",
      "serverId": "85c56323-6fa9-3386-8a01-6480fb634889"
